{"tid":762991,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人養開金魚？救救我的金魚🙏🏻","createTime":"2018-07-31T17:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T06:03:04.000Z","uid":13167,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e813f26b22608375f1085d45aa0b8f62930cdb11","tid":762991,"uid":13167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:52:50.000Z","msg":"養左佢大約一年<br />\n平時幾日至一星期換一次水<br />\n今日開發現佢：<br />\n1）甩鱗<br />\n2）神情有時呆滯<br />\n3）有時游得好奇怪 同平時唔同<br />\n4）出現過類似打冷震情況<br />\n<br />\n即時幫佢換水同埋拎走哂魚缸內裝飾<br />\n神情同游水狀況都即時得到改善<br />\n上網睇可能係患左<br />\n1）細菌性爛尾、爛鰭症 或<br />\n2）細菌性鰓病<br />\n<br />\n請問可以買咩藥或者有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日都打算去金魚街問下d水族店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/015218_dd373973bded66d014e601c0637a97a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F015218_dd373973bded66d014e601c0637a97a2.png&h=ba4dd18c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/015226_3c03cec21e7b0223b54deb064f790222.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F015226_3c03cec21e7b0223b54deb064f790222.png&h=0c4ed689&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bc16caa839f6d3bd10bf84f8a8ec043d789275f","tid":762991,"uid":6275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"好QQ 幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e146546eda85065f5ded04c1b64e9c6292050a7","tid":762991,"uid":13167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bc16caa839f6d3bd10bf84f8a8ec043d789275f","tid":762991,"uid":6275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"好QQ 幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好