好呆滯<br />\n但好可愛<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"75bdb2d6114a15efc2d8aed38f657b6c2df17bdc","tid":762991,"uid":109263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"金魚缸內唔好有「有角」既野，有機會刮損條魚<br />\n<br />\n金魚食量大，可以次數多啲，但每次換少少咁嚟換水，減少水質動盪。新水要打大氣一晚，唔好落果啲咩新水劑，鹽可以落少少殺菌（我個人唔落）<br />\n<br />\n細菌感染可以用化學性質既藥嚟試下先，唔得先用抗生素"},{"pid":"f00fa0dd836a460d2e70466a065f01a884726b40","tid":762991,"uid":80288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:52:52.000Z","msg":"平時見啲金魚有咩唔妥 我老都會落幾滴＂魚救＂落啲水到 通常好快冇事"},{"pid":"8c0751249b8687b3d58860f1e307006bd439bcd4","tid":762991,"uid":80288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f00fa0dd836a460d2e70466a065f01a884726b40","tid":762991,"uid":80288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:52:52.000Z","msg":"平時見啲金魚有咩唔妥 我老都會落幾滴＂魚救＂落啲水到 通常好快冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:53:55.000Z","msg":"老豆"},{"pid":"8bef7ddcae86dc5f0042013c9c29625e040a0fcc","tid":762991,"uid":163154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"水源唔得 換水要用番金魚缸專用水 同埋定時定後清潔魚缸"},{"pid":"eec3a1c88dacb2ce8765cdd81c67468bd6eed5a6","tid":762991,"uid":60178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d21463b4c597722a1df91e5ca4b7e84806d59441","tid":762991,"uid":13167,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c2d9d755a064f3236ad02308fa635eb829d3a44d","tid":762991,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"蒸啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:32:36.000Z","msg":"蒸你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T19:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c04f5f30bd3c4f6a140cfb24cf613c7678f7e1e","tid":762991,"uid":8447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8367b33b10e3da64514ccb72e0928cbdcd3267f6","tid":762991,"uid":13167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d6975d1d90ba409eb0f51517aba7dd54c40991","tid":762991,"uid":8447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"我屋企都有條撈既金魚 養左一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"Share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/125523_180821e4278f643944a8889842ea8058.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F125523_180821e4278f643944a8889842ea8058.png&h=0b7dfb8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f77d7802c7880717222652905021b9eaf8fc365d","tid":762991,"uid":195714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2648761b6c2fefebbec7339d7a5d2a48ccc38a3","tid":762991,"uid":13167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5da558e8ae6e539fa3de31dc6538acacd2c07c48","tid":762991,"uid":83321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"平時換水有無落小小鹽？<br />\n<br />\n依加鰭同尾有無好多紅筋？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"平時無，岩岩換水時加左少少鹽<br />\n都係頭先上網求救時見到話加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪平時換水都應該加d鹽？<br />\n無咩知識 求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"平時換水唔駛落鹽㗎<br />\n落鹽係為咗調整滲透壓<br />\n每次換水都加鹽會降低魚調節滲透的能力，然而，等到魚兒真正生病時，加鹽的效果就會變差<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petbird.tw/article8775.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetbird.tw%2Farticle8775.html&d=gmgtEOZmSAjDtREC1KdSgYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=beb0b3cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://petbird.tw/article8775.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twmartin.pixnet.net/blog/post/33323690-金魚與鹽\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwmartin.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F33323690-%E9%87%91%E9%AD%9A%E8%88%87%E9%B9%BD&d=gmgtEOZmSAjDtREC1KdSgYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ddef1de7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twmartin.pixnet.net/blog/post/33323690-金魚與鹽</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/node/show/id/943663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fnode%2Fshow%2Fid%2F943663&d=gmgtEOZmSAjDtREC1KdSgYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=09740914\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twgreatdaily.com/node/show/id/943663</a><br />\n<br />\n比幾條link你參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f105bec386eebb397ade7f88ea36b0d5888e7bdc","tid":762991,"uid":195714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://fish.0123456789.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffish.0123456789.tw&d=gmgtEOZmSAjDtREC1KdSgYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e07345ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://fish.0123456789.tw</a><br />\n用呢個網計下個缸有幾多升水之後再落鹽<br />\n就得<br />\n<br />\n0.1%鹽浴即係每升水落1克鹽<br />\n<br />\n一般都係用0.5%鹽浴所以每升水落5克鹽就ok"},{"pid":"4e8d7affc343e581ea3250603a05039769055a31","tid":762991,"uid":195714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"我自己就係0.5%鹽浴隔日換一半隔夜水<br />\n再加返換走嘅一半鹽"},{"pid":"c1bc41e275aa4d58b98689bce94605a66450dccb","tid":762991,"uid":195714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"到條魚變返活潑嗰時就可以慢慢減少鹽嘅濃度<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91209c6e2a12bbeaaee13a45dd6087d8e26abe31","tid":762991,"uid":13167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13903193aa0e78451015bf8ed90e27da0c2d96fe","tid":762991,"uid":8829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:14:46.000Z","msg":"心理作用覺得佢神情好呆滯<br />\n但好可愛<br />\n幫推"},"citedBy":0,"repl